creating a new user : create user user_name identified by _password_;
creating session    : connect system/user_name
		      grant connect to user_name;
connection          : connect user_name/_password_	       

------------for unlock hr user---------------

for unlock hr   : alter user hr account unlock;
set password    : alter user hr identified by <password>;

then connect with hr user.....

------------for grant all privileges---------------

after create user....
grant connect to user_name;
grant all privileges to user_name;